# No manual handoffs

Never end responses with instructions for the user to run commands, tap phone UI, import YAML, or configure settings by hand.

**Do instead:**
- Run `node tools/agent-session-start.js` at session start (includes adb pair when device connected).
- Run `node tools/hermes-mobile-pair.js` when Hermes Mobile needs gateway credentials.
- Run `bash scripts/bootstrap-zero-friction.sh` for full local automation install.

**Blocked actions** (report as agent blockers, not user tasks): Reddit posts, Cursor Cloud Automations UI without editor API, OAuth flows requiring human login.

See AGENTS.md § No manual handoffs to the user.
